{"tid":1878943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北韓官員到過中国違反隔離令  立即槍決","createTime":"2020-02-14T01:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T07:18:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d0aab29bfebfa6a7b27de718ab33d7fb93d3a094","tid":1878943,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:42:55.000Z","msg":"南韓「東亞日報」今天報導，北韓一名貿易官員到過中國之後，回國沒有遵守隔離命令，立即遭到槍決。<br />\n<br />\n報導指稱，北韓由於和中國接壤，疫情爆發後相當緊張，已經在1月30日封鎖邊境，並要求在這之前到過中國，或與中國人士接觸者必須無條件隔離14天。<br />\n<br />\n北韓領導人金正恩更下令，若在隔離期間脫離指定場所，將被軍法處置。<br />\n<br />\n所有政府人員與住在北韓的外國人士，都必須無條件遵守隔離令。<br />\n<br />\n然而，這個月初卻有一名北韓貿易官員回國後違反命令，跑去大眾澡堂，被得知後立即遭到逮捕槍決。<br />\n<br />\n報導也指出，另有一名國家安全局官員因為想要隱瞞曾經到過中國的事實，遭下放到農場勞動改造。<br />\n<br />\n北韓目前幾乎已經完全關閉與中國的邊境、班機縮減，道路與鐵路也大多關閉或限制通行，並禁止所有外國觀光客入境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ksnews.com.tw/index.php/news/contents_page/0001343891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ksnews.com.tw%2Findex.php%2Fnews%2Fcontents_page%2F0001343891&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=ec3a7738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ksnews.com.tw/index.php/news/contents_page/0001343891</a><br />\n<br />\n北韓至今尚未傳出有武漢肺炎確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n平壤政府昨天宣布施行更嚴格的隔離令，把隔離期從14天延長至一個月。"},{"pid":"d8182ac4ee794c75b58afa551b33140a30d023a4","tid":1878943,"uid":153144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:44:53.000Z","msg":"唔係話有幾單咩"},{"pid":"5332da24b1607a302f7c46e39c60b870fd91e4b1","tid":1878943,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8182ac4ee794c75b58afa551b33140a30d023a4","tid":1878943,"uid":153144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:44:53.000Z","msg":"唔係話有幾單咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:45:53.000Z","msg":"官方宣稱冇"},{"pid":"e31b8214537285934cf4d59b40f00affdd010b8d","tid":1878943,"uid":30145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8182ac4ee794c75b58afa551b33140a30d023a4","tid":1878943,"uid":153144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:44:53.000Z","msg":"唔係話有幾單咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:48:49.000Z","msg":"直接犬決左/迫擊炮處理 仲邊度會有"},{"pid":"6de935ef29050ddf766fa0d4dc829cace5e8c615","tid":1878943,"uid":335834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"有咩外國人士會住北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n被佢綁架嗰啲？"},{"pid":"a01a351969d203a9aa2f978173af863d1265509d","tid":1878943,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:09:40.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85538c7e73a79abf46fc158119f689a08e20447","tid":1878943,"uid":191926,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:11:19.000Z","msg":"叫金將軍 頂陳肇始個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febf0ebd5115238dd7ae05fb7b8cdef8f58726ca","tid":1878943,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268e8229c5b609f213e7c633d9b385d3b0ed5e60","tid":1878943,"uid":132918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:13:47.000Z","msg":"危機意識比支那好<br />\n明知要隔離重去公眾澡堂，惡意散佈病毒危害國家安全槍斃好正路。"},{"pid":"cba3e9d8f562fee3bdd886d35ea2ee30a20f5b13","tid":1878943,"uid":58852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e996cc9fc85d38f27d743e362299e0558d8